{UTF-8}
Conversion factor=0.1
	~	dimensionless
	~		|

Predation rate=0.01
	~	1/(Animals*Year)
	~		|

Predations=Prey*Predators*Predation rate
	~	Animals/Year
	~		|

Predator births=Predations*Conversion factor
	~	Animals/Year
	~		|

Predator death rate=0.1
	~	1/Year
	~		|

Predator deaths=Predators*Predator death rate
	~	Animals/Year
	~		|

Predators= INTEG (Predator births-Predator deaths,
		50)
	~	Animals
	~		|

Prey= INTEG (Prey births-Predations,
		500)
	~	Animals
	~		|

Prey birth rate=0.1
	~	1/Year
	~		|

Prey births=Prey*Prey birth rate
	~	Animals/Year
	~		|

********************************************************
	.Control
********************************************************~
		Simulation Control Parameters
	|

FINAL TIME  = 200
	~	Year
	~	The final time for the simulation.
	|

INITIAL TIME  = 0
	~	Year
	~	The initial time for the simulation.
	|

SAVEPER  = 
        TIME STEP
	~	Year [0,?]
	~	The frequency with which output is stored.
	|

TIME STEP  = 1
	~	Year [0,?]
	~	The time step for the simulation.
	|

